            </div>

            <h1 class="heading-display text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl mb-6">
              AI for <em>Real Estate</em> Agents
            </h1>

            <p class="text-xl text-stone leading-relaxed mb-4">
              The first agent to respond wins 78% of the time.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-stone leading-relaxed mb-8">
              AI ensures you're always first—responding to leads in seconds, nurturing prospects automatically, and never letting a deal slip through the cracks. Whether you're in Huntsville, Florence, or anywhere in North Alabama, AI gives you the follow-up consistency of a large team without the overhead.
            </p>

            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
              <a href="/#contact" class="btn-primary inline-flex">
                <span>Get a Free Consultation</span>
              </a>
              <a href="#solutions" class="btn-secondary inline-flex">
                <span>See How It Works</span>
              </a>
